<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,920,1484]" pageId="7" pageNumber="449">
<emphasis box="[198,317,1265,1290]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="449">Diagnosis</emphasis>
. Arms approximately 3–4 times 
<collectionCode box="[700,748,1265,1291]" country="France" name="Musee de Lectoure" pageId="7" pageNumber="449">ML</collectionCode>
. Arm formula variable. Funnel organ W-shaped. Gills with 5–8 lamellae per inner demibranch and 6–8 lamellae per outer demibranch. LLI 6–16 (mean 10). Maximum spermatophore length 102, maximum SpLI 110, maximum number of spermatophores 28. Mature males without enlarged suckers. Integument smooth.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,920,1484]" pageId="7" pageNumber="449">
<emphasis box="[198,309,1420,1445]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="449">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species differs from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hoyle" authorityYear="1885" box="[611,831,1420,1445]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Octopodidae" genus="Benthoctopus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Octopoda" pageId="7" pageNumber="449" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="levis">
<emphasis box="[611,831,1420,1445]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="449">Benthoctopus levis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by the funnel organ (
<collectionCode box="[1079,1123,1420,1446]" pageId="7" pageNumber="449">VV</collectionCode>
in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hoyle" authorityYear="1885" box="[1159,1245,1420,1445]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Octopodidae" genus="Benthoctopus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Octopoda" pageId="7" pageNumber="449" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="levis">
<emphasis box="[1159,1245,1420,1445]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="449">B. levis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) and arm length (shorter in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hoyle" authorityYear="1885" box="[279,365,1459,1484]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Octopodidae" genus="Benthoctopus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Octopoda" pageId="7" pageNumber="449" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="levis">
<emphasis box="[279,365,1459,1484]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="449">B. levis</emphasis>
